Cell["\<\
The returned matrix is dense; for an explicit sparse form wrap the result \
with SparseArray.\
\>", "Notes",
 CellID->806105380,ExpressionUUID->"8884c178-5625-4c65-b1ff-f9a4ac329882"],

Cell["\<\
FlatMetric is a thin convenience over DiagonalMatrix[Join[ConstantArray[1, \
p], ConstantArray[-1, q]]]; it is most useful as the input metric to \
GammaMatrices, CliffordBasis, and CliffordCanonicalBasis.\
\>", "Notes",
 CellID->209222405,ExpressionUUID->"f74c8e10-04c8-4142-a128-1fd870d906ac"]
}, Dynamic[CurrentValue[
 EvaluationNotebook[], {TaggingRules, "Openers", "NotesSection"}, Closed]]]],

